    <briefdescription>
<para>The <ref refid="struct_x_usb_ps___config" kindref="compound">XUsbPs_Config</ref> structure contains configuration information for the USB controller. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This structure only contains the basic configuration for the controller. The caller also needs to initialize the controller for the DEVICE mode using the <ref refid="struct_x_usb_ps___device_config" kindref="compound">XUsbPs_DeviceConfig</ref> data structures with the <ref refid="group__usbps_1ga6daace32113a806a6822a6d5943a93f4" kindref="member">XUsbPs_ConfigureDevice()</ref> function call </para>    </detaileddescription>
